title: My Runes
body: I have a problem. I have a lvl 13 account and I have T2 runes, I can't add my runes to my runes page no matter what I do. Can someone help me please.  :(

replies.body:
Since this is something specific to your account, I recommend writing into our account specialists by [submitting a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new). We'll be able to better assist you there.

Let me know if you have any questions.
